-------
 Run
-------

This explain howto run Ardesia on windows.
Simply click on the ardesia under the menu.

In the same position you can execute curtain
and  spotlighter.exe.

In oder to record on windows:
- install vlc from http://www.videolan.org/vlc
- add the folder with the vlc.exe executable
  to the PATH environment


